Triode NOTICE
=============

This project (`triode`) includes code that is based on and/or derived from Hydra and hydra-synth.

Upstream projects
-----------------
- Hydra: https://github.com/hydra-synth/hydra
- hydra-synth: https://github.com/hydra-synth/hydra-synth

Attribution
-----------
- Original Hydra / hydra-synth authors include ojack and project contributors.
- Portions of this repository are adapted from hydra-synth source code and remain under AGPL-3.0-compatible terms.
- triode itself is distributed as AGPL-3.0-only; see `LICENSE`.

Significant upstream-derived components (modified/adapted)
----------------------------------------------------------
- `src/triode-synth.js` (adapted from hydra-synth runtime entrypoint patterns)
- `src/triode-source.js` (adapted from hydra-synth source/media handling)
- `src/hydra-source.js` (upstream-compatible source implementation with triode adaptations)
- `src/output.js` (upstream output/pipeline lineage with triode renderer changes)
- `src/generator-factory.js` (upstream transform/generator factory lineage)
- `src/generate-glsl.js` (upstream GLSL generation lineage)
- `src/glsl-source.js` (upstream shader-chain source lineage)
- `src/glsl/glsl-functions.js` (upstream function set lineage)
- `src/glsl/utility-functions.js` (upstream GLSL utility lineage)
- `src/glsl/renderpass-functions.js` (upstream renderpass helper lineage)
- `src/format-arguments.js` (upstream argument normalization lineage)
- `src/eval-sandbox.js` and `src/lib/sandbox.js` (upstream eval sandbox lineage)
- `src/lib/array-utils.js`, `src/lib/audio.js`, `src/lib/mouse-event.js`, `src/lib/video-recorder.js` (upstream utility lineage)
- `src/lib/mouse.js`, `src/lib/easing-functions.js`, `src/lib/screenmedia.js`, `src/lib/webcam.js` (upstream-origin files retained with minimal or no changes)

Further audit detail is tracked in `docs/compliance/agpl_audit.md`.
